rows.label: qst201312_msg0001
rows.name: You're searching for the children too?

rows.label: qst201312_msg0002
rows.name:
I was just told that they
apparently said they were going
to play around Lake Varna.

rows.label: qst201312_msg0003
rows.name:
That's too dangerous for children,
so I think it's a rumor, but...

rows.label: qst201312_msg0004
rows.name:
I wonder where they are now? I hope
they're not hurt, or hungry...
